KEYBOARD SHORTCUTS
tab = indent
shift + tab = un-indent
ctrl + z = undo
ctrl + y = redo
alt + z = wraps text
ctrl + / = comment or uncomment
alt + up/down = shuffles lines
double click word & enter key = will close the word in symbol

FILE STUFF
int = whole #
float = adds decimal
str = string
: .2f or .2g = round a set # of decimals (rounds up or down)
\ = new line
pwd = find path of file